snippet.title: Pro Philosopher 2: Demo Launch Teaser
snippet.description:
The comic political debate game "Pro Philosopher 2" now has a demo on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2120070/Pro_Philosopher_2_Governments__Grievances/
Get your first taste of what the game has to offer with a colorful cast of characters, expressive art, and dynamic, dramatic debates. And maybe get an early preview of something new...
